\id GAL - Plain English Version 
\h Galatians 
\toc3 Galatians 
\toc2 Galatians 
\toc1 Paul’s letter to the Christians at Galatia 
\mt1 The letter that Paul wrote to the Christians at Galatia  
\mt2 (The book in the Holy Bible called \bk Galatians\bk*)  
\imt1 About this letter  
\ip Paul wrote this letter about 2,000 years ago, about 20 years after Jesus went back to heaven, and it is now in the Holy Bible.  
\ip Paul wrote this letter to the Christians that were living in Galatia country. At that time Galatia was a part of the country that is now called Turkey.  
\ip God sent Paul to lots of countries to tell people about Jesus, and one of them was Galatia (see Acts 16:6). A lot of the Galatia people believed in Jesus and became Christians. Most of those new Christians were not Jews. (You see, Jesus belonged to the Jewish nation, so he was a Jew, and so were Peter, and Paul, and a lot of the other Christians at that time.)  
\ip After Paul left Galatia, some Jewish people went there and told the new Christians, “You can’t be a friend of God unless you become like us Jews. You men have to let somebody do a young man operation on you, and you all have to follow the Jewish law.”  
\ip The new Christians listened to those Jews and started to go wrong. Paul heard about it and it upset him, so he wrote this letter to get them to go the right way.  
\ip This letter has some very important messages for us today. It shows us that we need to trust Jesus and let the Holy Spirit control us, and not listen to anyone that says we have to go a different way.  
\cl Chapter  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 \w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w am|strong="G2532"\w* \w Paul|strong="G3972"\w*, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w this|strong="G3588"\w* letter \w is|strong="G3588"\w* \w from|strong="G1537"\w* \w me|strong="G1223"\w*. \w I|strong="G2532"\w*’m sending \w this|strong="G3588"\w* letter \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G2532"\w* \w Christians|strong="G2424"\w* \w in|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* churches \w in|strong="G2532"\w* Galatia country.  
\p \w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w am|strong="G2532"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w*’s special worker, \w but|strong="G2532"\w* \w it|strong="G2532"\w* wasn’\w t|strong="G3588"\w* \w a|strong="G2532"\w* \w man|strong="G3498"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w gave|strong="G2532"\w* \w me|strong="G1223"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w power|strong="G2316"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w be|strong="G2532"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w*’s special worker. \w It|strong="G2532"\w* wasn’\w t|strong="G3588"\w* \w any|strong="G3756"\w* mob \w of|strong="G1537"\w* \w people|strong="G3761"\w*. \w It|strong="G2532"\w* \w was|strong="G3588"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w*, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w our|strong="G2316"\w* \w father|strong="G3962"\w*. \w They|strong="G2532"\w* \w sent|strong="G2316"\w* \w me|strong="G1223"\w* \w out|strong="G1537"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* tell everybody \w about|strong="G2424"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w*. \w You|strong="G2532"\w* see, \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* really powerful. \w People|strong="G3761"\w* killed \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w*, \w but|strong="G2532"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w made|strong="G2316"\w* \w him|strong="G3588"\w* alive \w again|strong="G1453"\w*.   
\p
\v 2 \w Your|strong="G2532"\w* Christian friends \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w are|strong="G3588"\w* \w with|strong="G4862"\w* \w me|strong="G1473"\w* \w here|strong="G3956"\w*, \w they|strong="G2532"\w* \w all|strong="G3956"\w* \w say|strong="G3956"\w* \em hello\em* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G3956"\w*.   
\p
\v 3 \w I|strong="G1473"\w*’m asking \w God|strong="G2316"\w* \w our|strong="G2316"\w* \w father|strong="G3962"\w*, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2424"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w* \w our|strong="G2316"\w* leader, \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w be|strong="G2532"\w* \w good|strong="G2532"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w*, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w make|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* feel happy \w and|strong="G2532"\w* quiet inside \w yourselves|strong="G4771"\w*.  
\v 4 \w You|strong="G1325"\w* \w know|strong="G1537"\w*, \w we|strong="G2249"\w* \w all|strong="G2532"\w* \w did|strong="G2532"\w* \w bad|strong="G4190"\w* \w things|strong="G3588"\w*, \w but|strong="G2532"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2532"\w* \w took|strong="G2532"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* payback \w for|strong="G5228"\w* \w all|strong="G2532"\w* \w of|strong="G1537"\w* \w us|strong="G1325"\w*. \w He|strong="G2532"\w* \w died|strong="G3588"\w* instead \w of|strong="G1537"\w* \w us|strong="G1325"\w*, \w so|strong="G2532"\w* \w now|strong="G2532"\w* \w he|strong="G2532"\w* \w can|strong="G1325"\w* save \w us|strong="G1325"\w* \w from|strong="G1537"\w* \w this|strong="G3588"\w* \w bad|strong="G4190"\w* world \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w we|strong="G2249"\w* \w live|strong="G2532"\w* \w in|strong="G2596"\w*. \w That|strong="G3588"\w* \w is|strong="G3588"\w* \w what|strong="G3588"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w*, \w our|strong="G2316"\w* \w father|strong="G3962"\w*, wanted \w him|strong="G3588"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w do|strong="G2532"\w*.  
