\s1 Don’t listen to the wrong story  
\p
\v 6-7 But now listen, you mob. You are giving me a big shock. A little while ago I told you the true story about God, but now you are already listening to other people, and they are turning you away from God. You are forgetting the good news we told you, and now you are listening to a different story that other people are telling you. They say it is good news, but it is not. We told you the proper good news about Jesus Christ. He loves you, and he is very good to you, and God used him to bring you into his family. But that other mob are trying to change this story into another story, and they call it \em good news\em*. But really, there is only one good news story. They are just messing you up.  
\v 8 Listen, don’t \w let|strong="G1510"\w* anybody teach \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w a|strong="G2532"\w* different story \w that|strong="G3739"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w not|strong="G1510"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* proper \w good|strong="G2097"\w* \w news|strong="G2097"\w* \w that|strong="G3739"\w* \w we|strong="G2249"\w* taught \w you|strong="G5210"\w*. \w I|strong="G1473"\w* pray \w that|strong="G3739"\w* \w God|strong="G2532"\w* \w will|strong="G1510"\w* punish \w anyone|strong="G3739"\w* \w that|strong="G3739"\w* teaches \w a|strong="G2532"\w* different message, \w no|strong="G2532"\w* matter \w who|strong="G3739"\w* \w it|strong="G2532"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w*, \w even|strong="G2532"\w* \w if|strong="G1437"\w* \w it|strong="G2532"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* \w us|strong="G2097"\w*, \w or|strong="G2228"\w* \w an|strong="G2532"\w* angel messenger \w from|strong="G1537"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* \w sky|strong="G3772"\w*.  
\v 9 \w I|strong="G3739"\w* \w will|strong="G1510"\w* \w say|strong="G3004"\w* \w it|strong="G2532"\w* \w again|strong="G3825"\w*. \w If|strong="G1487"\w* \w anyone|strong="G5100"\w* teaches \w a|strong="G5613"\w* story \w that|strong="G3739"\w* \w is|strong="G1510"\w* different \w from|strong="G3844"\w* \w the|strong="G2532"\w* story \w that|strong="G3739"\w* \w we|strong="G3739"\w* \w told|strong="G3004"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w*, \w the|strong="G2532"\w* story \w that|strong="G3739"\w* \w you|strong="G5210"\w* \w believed|strong="G2532"\w*, \w I|strong="G3739"\w* want \w God|strong="G3004"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* properly punish \w that|strong="G3739"\w* \w person|strong="G3739"\w*.   
\p
\v 10 \w I|strong="G1063"\w*’m \w not|strong="G3756"\w* \w trying|strong="G2212"\w* \w to|strong="G2212"\w* \w make|strong="G3756"\w* \w people|strong="G1510"\w* happy \w with|strong="G2316"\w* \w me|strong="G2212"\w*, \w I|strong="G1063"\w*’m \w trying|strong="G2212"\w* \w to|strong="G2212"\w* \w make|strong="G3756"\w* \w God|strong="G2316"\w* happy \w with|strong="G2316"\w* \w me|strong="G2212"\w*. \w I|strong="G1063"\w* work \w for|strong="G1063"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G1510"\w* \w Christ|strong="G5547"\w* \w now|strong="G1510"\w*, \w so|strong="G1063"\w* \w it|strong="G1063"\w* doesn’\w t|strong="G3588"\w* matter \w to|strong="G2212"\w* \w me|strong="G2212"\w* \w if|strong="G1487"\w* \w some|strong="G3588"\w* \w people|strong="G1510"\w* aren’\w t|strong="G3588"\w* happy \w when|strong="G1510"\w* \w I|strong="G1063"\w* talk straight like \w this|strong="G3588"\w*.   
\s1 Paul’s message came from Jesus Christ, not from people  
\p
\v 11-12 You see, my Christian friends, I want you to understand this. Jesus Christ himself told me that good news. No man or woman made up that message. It came from Jesus himself, and after Jesus told me that message, I told it to you.   
\p
\v 13 \w It|strong="G2532"\w* \w was|strong="G3588"\w* \w like|strong="G2596"\w* \w this|strong="G3588"\w*. \w You|strong="G3754"\w* \w have|strong="G2532"\w* heard \w what|strong="G3588"\w* \w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w was|strong="G3588"\w* \w like|strong="G2596"\w* \w before|strong="G1722"\w*. \w At|strong="G1722"\w* \w that|strong="G3754"\w* \w time|strong="G4218"\w*, \w I|strong="G2532"\w* didn’\w t|strong="G3588"\w* believe \w in|strong="G1722"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2532"\w*. \w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w was|strong="G3588"\w* \w a|strong="G2532"\w* Jew, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w believed|strong="G3588"\w* everything \w that|strong="G3754"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* Jews believe. \w And|strong="G2532"\w* \w you|strong="G3754"\w* \w know|strong="G1722"\w* \w about|strong="G2596"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w things|strong="G3588"\w* \w that|strong="G3754"\w* \w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w did|strong="G2532"\w* \w at|strong="G1722"\w* \w that|strong="G3754"\w* \w time|strong="G4218"\w*. \w I|strong="G2532"\w* \w made|strong="G2316"\w* \w a|strong="G2532"\w* lot \w of|strong="G2316"\w* trouble \w for|strong="G1063"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* Christian \w people|strong="G3588"\w*. \w I|strong="G2532"\w* tried hard \w to|strong="G2532"\w* stop \w them|strong="G3588"\w* \w from|strong="G2532"\w* \w following|strong="G2596"\w* \w Jesus|strong="G2532"\w*.\x * \xo 1:13 \xt Acts 8:3; 22:4-5; 26:9-11\x*   
\p
\v 14 \w You|strong="G1722"\w* see, \w our|strong="G2532"\w* Jewish grand-fathers told \w us|strong="G1722"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w way|strong="G1722"\w* \w we|strong="G2532"\w* Jewish \w people|strong="G1085"\w* \w had|strong="G2532"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w live|strong="G5225"\w*, \w and|strong="G2532"\w* \w I|strong="G1473"\w* tried \w hard|strong="G4183"\w* \w to|strong="G2532"\w* \w live|strong="G5225"\w* \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w way|strong="G1722"\w*. \w I|strong="G1473"\w* \w was|strong="G3588"\w* becoming \w a|strong="G2532"\w* \w better|strong="G4183"\w* Jew \w than|strong="G4183"\w* \w most|strong="G4183"\w* \w of|strong="G2532"\w* \w my|strong="G1722"\w* mates, \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w other|strong="G4183"\w* Jews \w that|strong="G3588"\w* \w were|strong="G3588"\w* \w the|strong="G1722"\w* \w same|strong="G2532"\w* age \w as|strong="G1722"\w* \w me|strong="G1473"\w*.\x * \xo 1:14 \xt Acts 22:3\x*  
